title: Cam Newton, Dak Prescott, Odell Beckham Jr., Blazin' 5
itunes:title: Cam Newton, Dak Prescott, Odell Beckham Jr., Blazin' 5
description:
Colin Cowherd weighs in on Cam Newton's continued struggles and explains why it's proof that Dak Prescott deserves to get paid. He sounds off on Odell Beckham Jr. taking shots at Jets DC Gregg Williams and shares his Blazin' 5 for Week 2 in the NFL. Also, he tells you the real reason the Patriots brought in Antonio Brown! 

Guests: Albert Breer, Geoff Schwartz, T.J. Houshmandzadeh, Urban Meyer, Jason McIntyre
